flowchart LR
    Sample["采样 busy/temp/power"] --> Filter["滑动平均 / EMA"]
    Filter --> Judge{"超过阈值?"}
    Judge -->|连续 N 次高负载| Up["请求升 OPP"]
    Judge -->|连续 M 次低负载| Down["请求降 OPP"]
    Judge -->|中间区间| Hold["保持当前 OPP"]
    Up --> Residency["min residency / cooldown"]
    Down --> Residency
    Hold --> Sample
    Residency --> Sample
